            "The city street had scavengers picking through trash for recyclables.",
            "A scavenger bird waited for a meal after the storm."
          ],
          "collocations": ["scavenger hunt", "scavenger at", "scavenger bird"],
          "synonyms": ["forager", "carrier", "garbage picker"],
